   <description>
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="/img/posts/2019-10-10-story-meta-story/pict.png" alt="image" height="251" style="vertical-align: -10px; margin: -3px -3px -3px -3px;" width="251" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are stories and there are &lt;span style="font-weight: bold"&gt;meta-stories&lt;/span&gt; &amp;ndash; stories &lt;span style="font-style: italic"&gt;about&lt;/span&gt; the stories.  Because I care about you (the reader) I must tell &lt;span style="font-weight: bold"&gt;meta-stories&lt;/span&gt; as well as stories.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Consider learning that an ancient tome you found in a used bookstore was written as its author slowly went insane.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href="http://stephenfoster.us/2019/10/story-meta-story.html?utm_source=all&amp;amp;utm_medium=RSS"&gt;&lt;em&gt;More&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description></item>
